                    <span>I have Stephen Mitchell's version of the Tao Te Ching which I just received and read today and I have to say I was VERY disappointed in it. I would say it's not so much a translation as a paraphrase of his own thoughts with some of those of Lao Tzu blended in to make it seem like a translation of the Tao Te Ching. This is a much, much better version.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A beautiful piece of work</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
